{"id":6409,"date":"2026-04-19T17:56:30","date_gmt":"2026-04-19T17:56:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/?page_id=6409"},"modified":"2026-06-03T16:19:45","modified_gmt":"2026-06-03T16:19:45","slug":"agriexchange","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/internationalfarmunion.com\/platforms\/agriexchange\/","title":{"rendered":"AgriExchange"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"6409\" class=\"elementor elementor-6409\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5e5458bc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5e5458bc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ccc4af2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-cherito-about\" data-id=\"2ccc4af2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"cherito-about.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"about-one section-space\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"about-one__bg\"><\/div><!-- \/.about-one__bg -->\r\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"row gutter-y-50\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"sec-title wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"sec-title__title\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAgriExchange - Trade\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3><!-- \/.sec-title__title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.sec-title -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__text-box wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"about-one__text\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAgriExchange is the global trading and marketplace engine of the IFU ecosystem, now extended to include IFU Agritourism experiences.\n\nIt enables farmers, cooperatives, businesses, and buyers to buy and sell agricultural products, while also allowing farms and rural communities to offer agritourism experiences to local and international visitors.\n\nMore than a marketplace, AgriExchange is where products and places become opportunities, transactions, income, and cultural exchange.\n<BR><BR>\nAcross the agricultural world, two major opportunities are often underdeveloped:\n<BR><BR>\n\n1. <strong>Market Access Challenges<\/strong><BR>\n- Farmers struggle to reach reliable buyers<BR>\n- Buyers struggle to find trusted suppliers<BR>\n- Prices are inconsistent and often unfair<BR>\n- Supply chains lack transparency<BR><BR>\n2. Untapped Agritourism Potential<BR>\n- Farms have unique experiences to offer but lack visibility<BR>\n- Rural communities miss out on tourism income<BR>\n- Travelers struggle to find authentic agricultural experiences<BR><BR>\nAgriExchange was developed to solve both.\n\nIt is built on a simple principle:\n\nAgriculture should generate value not only through products\u2014but also through experiences.\n\nAgriExchange creates a dual marketplace where users can trade goods and discover agricultural experiences globally.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__text-box -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__inner__content\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner__content -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div><!-- \/.about-one__inner -->\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"about-one__button wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-duration=\"1500ms\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\"   class=\"cherito-btn\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__text\">AgriExchange Login<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--1\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--2\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cherito-btn__hover--3\"><\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"cherito-btn__hover cheri